                     <interp inst="t17180227-28-off140" type="offenceCategory" value="theft"></interp>
                     <interp inst="t17180227-28-off140" type="offenceSubcategory" value="grandLarceny"></interp>
               feloniously stealing 144 pair of Gloves, 8 pair of Thread Hose, 12 Muslin Neckcloths, 12 Knives and Forks, and other Goods, to the value of 34 l.
            </rs> the Property of 
               
                  <persName id="t17180227-28-victim150" type="victimName">
                     James 
                     Butler 
                  <interp inst="t17180227-28-victim150" type="surname" value="Butler"></interp>
